Let $n$ be a non-negative integer representing the size of input. The time complexity of the following piece of code is $\Theta(n^2)$.

```c
int func(int n) {
    int sum = 0;
    for (int i = 1; i < n; i *= 2)
        for (int j = 0; j < i; j++)
            sum++;
    return sum;
}
```

